parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ABS system can cause extended stopping distances, loss of control, and accidents, which can lead to injuries or fatalities.

the brake pedal goes to the floor

the brakes lock up

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the windshield wipers can cause poor visibility while driving in inclement weather, leading to accidents or near-misses.
symptoms: Windshield wipers work intermittently

or fail to operate at all

symptoms: The airbag warning light is illuminated

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The illumination of the airbag light can indicate a malfunction in the airbag system, which can lead to the failure of the airbag to deploy in a crash.
symptoms: The airbag warning light is illuminated
the airbag system is malfunctioning
the airbag computer module needs to be replaced.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the seatbelt to restrain the occupant properly can lead to serious injuries or fatalities in a crash.
